entries.title_d: Intercept the Rebel operative as they make their escape through the Dantooine system.
entries.title: Dantooine System: The Long Run
entries.quest_target_d: The Rebel craft seen fleeing from the Endor System.
entries.quest_location_d: Coming out of the Isyrn's Veil hyperspace point making a run for the nearest Rebel outpost
entries.quest_escort_d: A pair of Rebel X-Wing fighters, only the operative is important.
entries.failed_escape: \#pcontrast3 Kilnstrider: < \#pcontrast1 You let him get away Captain.  Failure seems to be a common thing among you mercenaries. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 All escorting craft have been destroyed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 An escorting craft has been destroyed, %DI remain. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.destroy_escort: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Primary objective destroyed, finish off any remaining escort. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.autorewardbody: By the authority of < Admiral Kilnstrider > you have been awarded a credit bonus to the sum of < 20000 > for < Elimination of a Rebel operative>
entries.assassinate_success: \#pcontrast3 Kilnstrider: <  \#pcontrast1 I congratulate you on your quick thinking Captain.  Whatever information they might have taken is not lost to the Rebel Alliance.  This operation is now concluded.  Kilnstrider out. \#pcontrast3 >
